    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MYSTiQUES is an antiquing game about the four worst women you’ve ever met. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gem, Aspen, Winnie and Barb run a failing antique store that can only be saved by one thing: 🔮✨<strong><i>psychic powers</i></strong>✨🔮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/c2947fa927d17ef8f1ceb76155149dcf.poster.avif?t=1743659004\" width=609 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/c2947fa927d17ef8f1ceb76155149dcf.webm?t=1743659004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻 Go on jobs to deceased estates, run-down motels and more to find valuable antiques to sell back at the shop. Or you can keep them, no one will notice</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻 Use Gem's ✨<i>psychic powers✨</i> to connect to the spirits left behind in antiques and uncover their secrets</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/9a38630511aa4733b37bf3f2cfe68f00.poster.avif?t=1743659004\" width=609 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/9a38630511aa4733b37bf3f2cfe68f00.webm?t=1743659004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 Flex your creativity in the shop, decorating the windows and displays with the treasures you find on jobs </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👗 Collect your dream wardrobe and curate cute retro looks </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/44d5c362a29ca20aa58834e2ce25327b.poster.avif?t=1743659004\" width=609 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235660/extras/44d5c362a29ca20aa58834e2ce25327b.webm?t=1743659004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💔 Investigate a mysterious local cult... but <i>DON'T</i> text your ex about it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💔 Seriously</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💔 ... unless? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
